    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snow War is a <strong>First Person Snowball</strong> game. No blood, no gore — just pure, chaotic fun where every hit counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/5a827e94e8aa43232ab5efdba8b3cb87.poster.avif?t=1769784000\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/5a827e94e8aa43232ab5efdba8b3cb87.webm?t=1769784000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/5a827e94e8aa43232ab5efdba8b3cb87.mp4?t=1769784000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find gadgets that protect you, boost your throws, or give you a temporary edge. Use them wisely — batteries don’t last forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/db4bd3d539fc64c7c8e4e3f6d8097052.poster.avif?t=1769784000\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/db4bd3d539fc64c7c8e4e3f6d8097052.webm?t=1769784000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585100/extras/db4bd3d539fc64c7c8e4e3f6d8097052.mp4?t=1769784000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? Battle across neon‑lit cities and pine‑covered forests. Climb the scoreboard and prove you’re the champion of the frozen wasteland.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❄️ <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic PvP FPS (First Person Snowball) action for up to 16 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free‑for‑all mode (team modes planned)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online or LAN play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline bots for practice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of power‑ups that change the flow of battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom servers with adjustable rules</p></li></ul>",
